    "description": "Prioritizing variants of uncertain significance with spatial genomic patterns in the 3D proteome.\n\nPrioritizing Variants of Uncertain Significance with Spatial Genomic Patterns.\n\nPIVOTAL: Prioritizing variants of uncertain significance with spatial genomic patterns in 3D proteome.\n\nPIVOTAL is a computational agent for prioritizing variants of uncertain significance (VUS), utilizing the spatial distribution of known disease mutations, evolutionary conservation and co-evolution on three-dimensional protein structures. To get started, search for your variants, protein or disease of interest.",
